	   <tr><td colspan=2>Also, if you are in a group with a warrior and a haste casting class, you can start nuking when the mob has only lost a quarter of it's life.&nbsp;&nbsp;That makes for some fast xp, and you will rarely get aggro'ed.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=1 >&nbsp;</td><td align=right valign=bottom>
	   <span style='font-weight: normal; font-size: 9px;'>[<a href=#top>Top</a>]</span></tr>
